Steps:
[AUTH] POST {{BACK_URL}}/connect/token → save Bearer token
[SETUP] prepare JSON body: {"name": "API Test Promo {{timestamp}}", "isActive": true, "priority": 15, "storeId": "{{STORE_ID}}", "type": "Promotion"}
[HTTP] POST {{BACK_URL}}/api/marketing/promotions with Authorization header and JSON body

[AUTH] POST {{BACK_URL}}/connect/token → save Bearer token
[SETUP] GET /api/marketing/promotions to obtain an existing promotion id → save as {{promo_id}}
[SETUP] prepare PUT body with updated name: {"id": "{{promo_id}}", "name": "UPDATED {{timestamp}}", "isActive": true}
[HTTP] PUT {{BACK_URL}}/api/marketing/promotions/{{promo_id}} with Authorization and JSON body

[AUTH] POST {{BACK_URL}}/connect/token → save Bearer token
[SETUP] POST /api/marketing/promotions to create test promotion → save {{promo_id}}
[HTTP] DELETE {{BACK_URL}}/api/marketing/promotions?ids={{promo_id}} with Authorization header
